~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~             {\textbf{Method of Undetermined Coefficients}}
{\bf{SOLUTION:}}
y(x)=y_{h}~+~y_{p}
{\text{Differential Equation:}}~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
y^{(5)}+2y^{(3)}+y'=2x+\sin(x)+\cos(x)
{\text{Homogeneous Case:}}~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
y^{(5)}+2y^{(3)}+y'=0
{\text{Characteristic Polynomial:}}~~~~~~~~~
r^5+2r^3+r=0
{\text{Solved Roots of polynomial:}}~~~~~~
\bigg[\{r\rightarrow 0\},\; \{r\rightarrow -i\},\; \{r\rightarrow -i\},\; \{r\rightarrow i\},\; \{r\rightarrow i\}\bigg]
